Package: climniche
Type: Package
Title: Niche Relative Climate Exposure
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bohao", "He", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bohao.he@polimi.it")
    )
Description: Measures projected climate exposure relative to a species'
    current reference niche estimated from occurrences, range maps or species
    distribution model suitability weights. The package reports Climatic
    Displacement, Niche Distance Shift, Climatic Reconfiguration and Niche
    Boundary Exceedance from current and future environmental data.
